# Hero Section Component

This is a `Hero` section component built with React, Framer Motion, react-mouse-follower, and Tailwind CSS. It is designed for showcasing audio products (e.g., headphones) with smooth animations and an interactive user experience.

## Table of Contents
- [Overview](#overview)
- [Features](#features)
- [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [Dependencies](#dependencies)
- [Customization](#customization)
- [Contributing](#contributing)
- [License](#license)

## Overview
The `Hero` component is designed to provide a visually appealing and interactive way to showcase a range of products. It includes animated transitions for text and images and a custom cursor that adapts to user interactions.

## Features
- Dynamic product showcase with smooth animations.
- Custom cursor effects for an engaging user experience.
- Responsive design suitable for mobile and desktop views.
- Easy to customize and extend with new products.
- Integrated WhatsApp link for direct contact.

## Dependencies
React: ^18.x.x
Framer Motion: ^10.x.x
react-mouse-follower: ^1.x.x
Tailwind CSS: ^3.x.x
react-icons: ^4.x.x

## Customization
Product Data: Update the hero array in the Hero component to change the displayed products.
Styling: Use Tailwind CSS classes to customize the look and feel of the section.
Animations: Modify the fadeUp function or motion properties for custom animation effects.
Cursor Effects: Adjust the mouseOptions in UpdateFollower for different cursor behaviors.
Contributing
Contributions are welcome! Please fork the repository and create a pull request with your changes.